<h1>Whitespace</h1>
<p class="green">You can use the br tag to break one line into multiple lines.</p>Br doesn't need a closing tag
Hello everyone!<br>We're using two lines now!

<br>Paragraph tag uses the "P" tag and must follow with "content".  Paragraphs must be closed with "/p"
<p>Hello everyone!</p>
<p>We're using two lines now!</p>

<h1>Inline/Block</h1>
br tag = Inline <br>(b) (em) (img) are all inline tags<br> P tag = block
<h1>Span and Div</h1>
<span>this is one line</span>
yep, one line
<div>this is one line</div>
yep, one line
<strong>this is one line</strong>
yep one line
